    <div class="container-std custom-content">
        <strong>THE PROJECT</strong>
        <p>The client lacked of branding and visual identity. The brief stated to create a logo with the use of
            typography and minimal or no graphic symbols, that should resonate a corporate and yet youthful feeling with
            the target group</p>

        <strong>MY ROLE</strong>
        <p>I was responsible for the creation of the identity from concept, mockups, source of typeface and colour
            palette, to final logo</p>

        <strong>THE RESULT</strong>
        <p>The client was very happy with the concept and the final design which was delivered in two versions</p>
    </div>

        <div class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32"></div>




