            <div class="custom-content">
                <h2>Typeface</h2>
                <p>The typeface Bryant Pro is a modern sans serif creating a clean, contemporary and minimalistic
                    approach as the same time, with its rounded corners gives the logo a young and fresh feeling.</p>

                <h2>Colours</h2>
                <p>The colours are vibrant and fresh but still with a degree of corporate touch symbolising growth,
                    ambition, stability, wisdom and confidence.</p>
            </div>

