        <div class="custom-content">

            <h2>CONCEPT</h2>
            <strong class="uppercase">Transformation</strong>
            <p>The logos represent the gradual transformation which Concern offers the young adults. The colour gradient
                represent both the platform and the progression in their career.</p>
            <p>A smaller sizes version was created with only four colour bars to enable to visualise the distinctive
                gradient</p>

